<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
      <div class="panel panel-info">
        <div class="panel-heading">
          <h2>The Pledge</h2>
          <p>Here's what we expect from you when you sign up for My Apnea, and what you can expect from us.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="pledge" class="panel-body">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <h3 class="center-block">You promise to...</h3>
              <div class="list-group">
                <div class="list-group-item">
                  <h4>Promise #1</h4>
                  <p>Some description of this promise...</p>
                </div>
                <div class="list-group-item">
                  <h4>Promise #2</h4>
                  <p>Another description for this promise...</p>
                </div>
                <div class="list-group-item">
                  <h4>Promise #3</h4>
                  <p>Yet another description, maybe a bit longer, detailing what you would be signing up for...</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <h3 class="center-block">We promise to...</h3>
              <div class="list-group">
                <div class="list-group-item">
                  <h4>Promise #1</h4>
                  <p>Some description of this promise...</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
          <%= link_to "I'm in!", new_registration_path(:user), class: 'btn btn-info btn-block' %>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>

</div>
